item.description:
After you install Rhize services, they are accessible, by default, on the following ports:
Service Default Port Admin UI localhost:3030 Grafana localhost:3001 Router localhost:4000 Keycloak localhost:8090 baas-alpha command line localhost:8080 URLs When you create DNS records, Rhize recommends the following URLs:
Service Domain Admin UI rhize-ui.&lt;YOUR_DOMAIN&gt; Keycloak rhize-auth.&lt;YOUR_DOMAIN&gt; GraphQL rhize-api.&lt;YOUR_DOMAIN&gt; NATS rhize-mqtt.&lt;YOUR_DOMAIN&gt; Grafana rhize-grafana.&lt;YOUR_DOMAIN&gt;
